      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Michael Byrne</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:235px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/MichaelB7\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/5/5f/MichaelByrne.jpg\" width=\"233\" height=\"233\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:MichaelByrne.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Michael B <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Michael (Mike) Byrne</b>,<br />\nan American now retired <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Certified_Public_Accountant\">certified public accountant</a> and finance manager, in 1983 graduated from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Pennsylvania\">University of Pennsylvania</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, and further chess player and computer chess aficionado. \nHe wrote computer chess articles for <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Reports\" title=\"Computer Chess Reports\">Computer Chess Reports</a> in the 90s, and served as moderator in <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>. He is member of the <a href=\"/Crafty\" title=\"Crafty\">Crafty</a> team around <a href=\"/Robert_Hyatt\" title=\"Robert Hyatt\">Robert Hyatt</a>. \nMore recently, he plays around with a derivative of <a href=\"/Senpai\" title=\"Senpai\">Senpai 1.0</a> by <a href=\"/Fabien_Letouzey\" title=\"Fabien Letouzey\">Fabien Letouzey</a>, dubbed <a href=\"/index.php?title=K%C5%8Dhai&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Kōhai (page does not exist)\">Kōhai</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>, \nthe <a href=\"/Gull\" title=\"Gull\">Gull 3</a> fork dubbed <a href=\"/Gull#Hawkeye\" title=\"Gull\">Hawkeye</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>, \nand a <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a> fork with <a href=\"/index.php?title=Cerebellum&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Cerebellum (page does not exist)\">Cerebellum</a> book, dubbed <a href=\"/index.php?title=McBrain&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"McBrain (page does not exist)\">McBrain</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> aka <b>McCain</b>, <b>Burnzie</b> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> and <b>Honey</b>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Articles\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Articles</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#1997_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1997 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">